#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2975
msgid ""
"'Priority' or 'PriorityID' specifies the name or id of the priority to be "
"used in the new ticket."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2979
