msgstr "Die Nummer der Aktivität die dem Prozessticket aktuell zugeordnet ist."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3476
msgid "ActivityDialogEntityID"
msgstr "ActivityDialogEntityID"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3478
msgid ""
"The ID of the Activity Dialog that is currently open for a process ticket."
msgstr ""
"Die Nummer des Aktivitätendialogs der dem Prozessticket aktuell zugeordnet "
"ist."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3483
msgid "Possible/PossibleNot Activity Dialog"
msgstr "Possible/PossibleNot Activity Dialog"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3485
msgid ""
"Here you can specify a list of Activity Dialog IDs. This list will limit the "
"possible Activity Dialogs that are offered to the user in the ticket zoom "
"mask."
msgstr ""
"Hier können Sie eine Liste von Aktivitätsdialogen-Nummern definieren. Diese "
"Liste beschränkt die möglichen Aktivitätsdialoge die dem Agenten in der "
"TicketZoom-Oberfläche angeboten werden."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3489
msgid ""
"'Possible' lists the Activity Dialogs that are allowed. The setting above "
"will only allow 'AD1' and 'AD3' of the list of configured Activity Dialogs."
msgstr ""
"'Möglich' listet die Aktivitätsdialoge auf, die erlaubt sind. Durch diese "
"Einstellung wird nur 'AD1' und 'AD3' in der Liste der konfigurierten "
"Aktivitätsdialoge angezeigt."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3493
msgid ""
"'PossibleNot' lists the Activity Dialogs that are not allowed. In the "
"example above, the setting will remove 'AD3' from the list of configured "
"Activity Dialogs."
msgstr ""
"'Nicht Möglich' listet die Aktivitätsdialoge auf, die nicht erlaubt sind. Im "
"oberen Beispiel wird diese Einstellung 'AD3' aus der Liste der "
"konfigurierten Aktivitätsdialoge entfernen."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3498
msgid ""
"If both 'Possible' and 'PossibleNot' are specified, the list of configured "
"Activity Dialogs will first be filtered by 'Possible', leaving only 'AD1' "
"and 'AD3' in our example. Then 'PossibleNot' will be applied and filter out "
"'AD3', so that only 'AD1' remains and is shown as a possible Activity Dialog "
"that the user can use."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3505
msgid ""
"If multiple ACL rules match, the intersection of all matching rules will be "
"calculated to determine the possible Activity Dialogs. Example:"
msgstr ""
"Wenn mehrere ACL-Regeln übereinstimmen, wird der Durchschnitt aller "
"passenden Regeln berechnet um die möglichen Aktivitätsdialoge zu bestimmen. "
"Beispiel:"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para><screen>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3511
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$Self->{TicketAcl}->{'001-ACL-Status'} = {\n"
"    Properties => {\n"
"        Ticket => {\n"
"            Status => 'new',\n"
"        }\n"
"    },\n"
"    Possible => {\n"
"        ActivityDialog => ['AD1', 'AD2', 'AD3', 'AD6', 'AD7'],\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
"$Self->{TicketAcl}->{'002-ACL-Queue'} = {\n"
"    Properties => {\n"
"        Ticket => {\n"
"            Queue => ['Raw']\n"
"        }\n"
"    },\n"
"    Possible => {\n"
"        ActivityDialog => ['AD2', 'AD3', 'AD4', 'AD7'],\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
