#. type: Content of: <section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/administration/dynamicfields-configuration.xml:87
msgid ""
"This is the internal name of the field, used for example to show or hide a "
"field in one screen. Any modification of a field name (not recommended) "
"requires a manual update of the \"SysConfig\" settings where the field is "
"referenciated."
